      "reasoning": "Substituting N=(n_x,n_y) into x^2+y^2-sx+Ey=0 gives -E=(n_x^2+n_y^2-sn_x)/n_y. From step 3, n_x=u^2/(u^2+v^2), n_y=uv/(u^2+v^2), and n_x^2+n_y^2=u^2/(u^2+v^2). Therefore -E=(u^2(1-s)/(u^2+v^2))/(uv/(u^2+v^2))=u(1-s)/v.",
